room_title: Escape room "Escape the 1980's" by Steel Owl Room Adventures in Philadelphia
room_address: 111 S Independence Mall E, Philadelphia, PA 19106
room_description: You find yourselves stuck in a 1980's time warp. To return back to the future, you will have to unlock doors, hack into computer systems, solve musical puzzles and a lot more! You don't need any special knowledge about the 80's to play, just pay attention to detail and try to escape the room!
